body:
yeah, we definitely cannot merge this yet: https://github.com/openwhisk/openwhisk/pull/883.
It will break the UI.  I let James Dubee know already.
@dubeejw - do we have a defect for this already?  If not I can create one.

Example:
 wsk -i action get /whisk.system/samples/wordCount

```
    {
        "key": "sampleOutput",
        "value": "{ \"count\": 3 }"
    },
    {
        "key": "sampleInput",
        "value": "{ \"payload\": \"Five fuzzy felines\"}"
    },
```

should be:

```
   {
        "key": "sampleOutput",
        "value": {
            "count": 3
        }
    },
    {
        "key": "sampleInput",
        "value": {
            "payload": "Five fuzzy felines"
        }
    },
```
